<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>You're Offline - NOOSH.</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background-color: #FFC72C;
            color: #111111;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .offline-wrap { max-width: 420px; }
        .offline-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        .offline-message {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .offline-retry {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #111111;
            color: #FFC72C;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 2px solid #111111;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .offline-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="offline-wrap">
        <div class="offline-icon">📡</div>
        <h1 class="offline-title">NOOSH<span style="color:#111">.</span></h1>
        <p class="offline-message">
            You're currently offline. Check your connection and try again —
            your favourite shawarmas will still be here.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="offline-retry" onclick="window.location.reload(); return false;">
            Try Again
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>